# demo-simulation — track the docs (.md) and transcripts (.txt); ignore heavy,
# regenerable, or customer-adjacent binary media.
#   Videos: Devon's WhatsApp clips + screen recordings (large; reference/
#   customer-adjacent — see spec §9). ** matches the top-level and devon-videos/.
demo-simulation/**/*.mp4
demo-simulation/**/*.mov
demo-simulation/**/*.m4v
#   Chart stills / frame grabs (jpg + png crops).
demo-simulation/devon-videos/stills/
#   Generated validation overlays + plot exports (regenerate from benchvision-app/).
demo-simulation/*.png
